2009-09-19  Leonardo Ferreira Fontenelle  <leonardof@gnome.org>

	* AUTHORS, NEWS: Added to make autogen happy.
	* Makefile.am: Added support for automake, non-recursive.
	* autogen.sh: Added as part of support to the GNU Build System.
	* classix.in: Fixed path to data files. Simplified header.
	* classix/: Moved to src/, so that classix.in can be used to create classix.
	* configure.ac: Added initial support for autoconf.
	* src/main.py: Fixed path to data files.

